modName: CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack exterior 1024v1_1 and 2048v2
summary: Pack textures for personal use, I come to share with you.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://static2.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/49241-1-1388814813.jpg[/img][/center]
[line]
[center][size=3][color=#ffcc33]Video maked by izon87604[/color][/size][/center]

[center][youtube]AKKIiKOSa1k[/YouTube][/center]
[line]
[center][size=8][color=#ffcc33]Description[/color][/size][/center]
[line]

This texture pack is created for my own personal use, I would now like to share with you. The textures are made in 1024p dtx5 for Ver1_1 for best performance so should not have a noticeable fps consumption. Textures for High quality are made in 2048p and 4096p dtx5. Enjoy it! ;)

All textures are new from scratch, fully retouched, both textures and normal maps.
[color=#ffcc33]It is entirely my work, you can see it when you use it.[/color]


[line]
[center][size=6][color=#ffcc33]About versions[/color][/size][/center]
[line]


[color=#fe2e2e][b]For Low end CPU. Best Performance[/b][/color]

*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack exterior 1024v1_1
*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Interior 1024_2048v1_1
*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Roads 2048v1_1

[color=#fe2e2e][b]For High end CPU. Best Quality[/b][/color]

*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Exterior 2048 v2
*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Interior 2048_4096v2
*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Roads 2048v1_1

[line]
[color=#fe2e2e][b]Optional for better inmersión:[/b][/color]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49538/?]*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Series[/url]
*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Series Rocks and Mountains
*.CAD25 Landscape Texture Series Dirtcliffs and Tundra Moss
[line]
[heading]Changes and Updates.[/heading]
* Ice and bridges exterior will not be retextured. There are many on the nexus page you can use.
* For Road, you can use Ver1_1 maked in 2048p for this mod in all version compatible.
[line]
[heading]ADD 09/01/2014 CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Soft Parallax for the Roads 2048v1_1[/heading]
*.This file contains the meshes and the parallax heights for work with the roads. You need the main road file and overwrite with this. enjoy it
[heading]ADD 08/01/2014 Road Update Ver1.1[/heading]
*.The stones of the road have been updated for a more rustic and less washed.
[heading]ADD 03/01/2014 Ver2.0[/heading]
[color=#ffcc33]CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Exterior 2048 v2[/color]

* Texture changes 2048p. without roads, ice and bridges.
* NMM compatible.

[color=#ffcc33]CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Interior 2048_4096v2[/color]

* Texture change interior for caves and mines. 2048p ground and 4096 rocks, wall rocks.
* NMM Compatible.
[line]

[heading]ADD 01/01/2014 Ver1_1. Happy new year.[/heading]

[color=#ffcc33]CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Roads 2048v1_1[/color]

1.1 * Texture changes for roads , maked for this mod
* Changed dirt02 for better compatibility.
* Roads 2048p
* NMM Compatible. Enjoy it ;).

[color=#ffcc33]CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack exterior 1024v1_1[/color]

1.1 *. Fixed the folder structure for work with NMM
*. Removed folder mines.
*. Was left to the last ice, road and bridge (check for updates).
*.NMM Compatible.

[color=#ffcc33]CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Interior 1024_2048v1_1[/color]

1.1 *. Added mines folder.
*.Ground 1024p, rock and wall rocks 2048p.
*. NMM Compatible.

[color=#fe2e2e]The Old Versión 1.0 and New 1.1 is for best perfomance, and a good quality with a mínimum loose FPS.[/color]

[line]
[center][size=6][color=#ffcc33]Installation:[/color][/size][/center]
[line]

1. Use NMM o Manual, overwrite.
2. Enjoy it ;).
[line]

[line]

[color=#fe2e2e][b]Take your time and send a comment, so I know that I should change or improve. Ideas are welcome.[/b][/color]

Feel free to endorse and add your own screenshot if you want.
This file is a Nexus exclusive, should appreciate my decisión.
If you want use it for you post or some ( Only for Nexus exclusive) Remember link to my mod.

files.name: CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack exterior 1024v1
files.changelogHtml:
1.0 *. Changing Textures worked for the entire exterior is 1024p
*. Includes mines with ground textures in 1024 and 2048 for the rocks
*. Was left to the last ice, road and bridge (check for updates).

CAD25 Landscape Texture Pack Interior 1024_2048v1

1.0 *.Changing Textures worked for the entire interior
*.Ground textures in 1024p and 2048 for the rocks

The Versión 1.0 is for best perfomance, and a good quality with a mínimum loose FPS.
The next will be: Ice, roads and bridges.
